fields.name: SAMSUNG UE43TU7100KXXU 43 Smart 4K
fields.description: Don't settle for anything less than crystal clear colour. The Samsung UE43TU7100KXXU 43 Smart 4K Ultra HD HDR LED TV delivers pure colours, sharp contrast, and brilliant brightness. HDR displays the brightest and darkest colours in each frame, so everything from dimly lit dialogue scenes to nature documentaries look vivid and realistic.
